Title: OpenShoppingCart
Description:
Asp.Net 2.0 Components for manage a Shopping Cart on any eCommerce WebSites, the particularity of this project, it use Provider Pattern, strongly typed datagrid and many Strongly typed controls, buttons, repeaters and more.

this project move to http://code.google.com/p/openshopp
HomeWiki:
OpenShoppingCart is an open source project from team serialcoder.net http://www.serialcoder.net

This is a asp.net 2.0 component for manage shopping cart in any ecommerce website.
Based on provider pattern.

Many controls as associated with this project , typed datagrid, typed buttons, linkbuttons and more..

Discussion Forum : http://groups-beta.google.com/group/open-shopping-cart

Mailing List : open-shopping-cart@googlegroups.com

Demo website : http://open-shopping-cart.serialcoder.net
